. The species name, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Scarbrough &amp; Perez-Gelabert" authorityYear="2008" box="[628,752,1411,1435]" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Efferia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="27" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vinalensis">
<emphasis box="[628,752,1411,1435]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="26">vinalensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, refers to Viñales Valley, the 
<typeStatus box="[1108,1161,1412,1436]" pageId="27" pageNumber="26">type</typeStatus>
locality.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
